sentences: Jonathan Hunt (born 6 August 1986), known professionally as Joth Hunt, is an Australian Pentecostal Christian worship leader, singer-songwriter, producer and music director who primarily writes praise and worship songs.
Hunt has released two solo albums, titled To Exist (2002) and Make a Stand (2004).
